      <h3>🥕 Ingredient Parser</h3>
      Rust based ingredient parser. Stared in 2021, an intermittent project. Demo:
      <a href="https://ingredient.nickysemenza.com"
        >ingredient.nickysemenza.com</a
      >
      <h3>📸 photography</h3>
      <p>
        photojournalism and freelance work from 2013 - 2018. Lately just travel
        and photos of my food.
      </p>
      <iframe
        src="https://www.nicky.photos/frame/slideshow?key=wXtF6f&autoStart=1&captions=1&navigation=1&playButton=0&randomize=1&speed=2&transition=fade&transitionSpeed=1"
